version_description: Previous versions of the chords have the verse as D C G A, but the bassline clearly shows that these are incomplete chords. I play unaccompanied, so I play the full chords with the bass notes. If you  have any doubt about them, check out the bass tabs, and listen to the original to hear those  changes. I also include notes on hos to play the chorus riff together with the rhythm on unaccompanied guitar.
This version is based on (and I think in the same key as) this recording: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pqmTMiIMG74.

song_name: Cygnus X-1 Book Ii Hemispheres Vi The Sphere - A Kind Of Dream

version_description: A simple, easy to play version of the song based on this link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nEVDZl5UvN4.
The chords are based on the bass guitar part in the song. It should be correct.
